Exercise:
    Consider the following records:
        Product(String name, Category category, double price)
        Order(Long d, Customer customer, List<Product> product, LocalDate orderDate)
        public record Customer(String name)
    And the following enum Category:
        TOY, ELECTRONIC, STATIONARY
    Write a set of code snippets using the Stream API to return data in the following way:
        A) Orders made by each customer
        B) Total cost of each order
        C) Names of customers who bought toys
        D) Order IDs with total price above 500, sorted by date
        E) Total amount paid by each customer across all their orders
    Create a set of Product and Order objets to test the queries above.